PN,42401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779466274
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough to play in Championship
OL,4,Cplay-off final after Southampton
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,FSouthampton have been expelled from
OL,8,Fthe Championship play-offs in relation
OL,9,Fto spying charges, the English
OL,10,FFootball League (EFL) has announced.
OL,12,FMiddlesbrough will play Hull City at
OL,13,FWembley Stadium, with the game still
OL,14,Fset to go ahead on Saturday (23 May).
OL,16,FThe Saints were charged by the EFL
OL,17,Flast Friday (22 May) following
OL,18,Faccusations that a training session at
OL,19,FMiddlesbrough's Rockliffe Park complex
OL,20,Fwas observed two days before the sides
OL,21,Fmet in a play-off semi-final first leg.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
