OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779466274
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough to play in Championship
OL,4,Cplay-off final after Southampton
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,FSouthampton admitted spying on
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough earlier this month, as
OL,9,Fwell Oxford United in December 2025
OL,10,Fand Ipswich Town in April 2026.
OL,12,FThe first incident of spying was in
OL,13,FDecember 2025, shortly after Tonda
OL,14,FEckert became head coach.
OL,16,FSouthampton have confirmed to the
OL,17,FPress Association that they will
OL,18,Fappeal against the decision.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779466274
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough to play in Championship
OL,4,Cplay-off final after Southampton
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,FThey beat Middlesbrough 1-0 on
OL,8,Faggregate following the semi-finals
OL,9,Flast month.
OL,11,FIn a statement the EFL said: "An
OL,12,FIndependent Disciplinary Commission
OL,13,Fhas today expelled Southampton from
OL,14,Fthe Sky Bet Championship Play-Offs
OL,15,Fafter the Club admitted to multiple
OL,16,Fbreaches of EFL Regulations related to
OL,17,Fthe unauthorised filming of other
OL,18,FClubs' training.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779466274
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough to play in Championship
OL,4,Cplay-off final after Southampton
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,F"In addition, the Club has received a
OL,8,Ffour-point deduction that will be
OL,9,Fapplied to the 2026/27 Championship
OL,10,Ftable, alongside a reprimand in
OL,11,Frespect of all the charges.
OL,13,F"The effect of today's order is that
OL,14,FMiddlesbrough are reinstated into the
OL,15,F2026 Play-Offs and will proceed to the
OL,16,FPlay-Off Final against Hull City. The
OL,17,Ffinal remains scheduled for Saturday
OL,18,F23 May, with the kick-off time to be
OL,19,Fconfirmed.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779466274
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough to play in Championship
OL,4,Cplay-off final after Southampton
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,F"Southampton was first charged on
OL,8,FFriday 8 May, with further charges
OL,9,Fissued on Sunday 17 May in relation to
OL,10,Fadditional breaches during the 2025/26
OL,11,Fseason. Those additional charges arose
OL,12,Ffrom matters identified after the
OL,13,Finitial proceedings involving
OL,14,FMiddlesbrough were initiated.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779466274
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough to play in Championship
OL,4,Cplay-off final after Southampton
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,F"Southampton admitted breaches of
OL,8,FRegulations requiring Clubs to act
OL,9,Fwith the utmost good faith and
OL,10,Fprohibiting the observation of another
OL,11,FClub's training session within 72
OL,12,Fhours of a scheduled match. The
OL,13,Fadmitted breaches concern fixtures
OL,14,Fagainst Oxford United in December
OL,15,F2025, Ipswich Town in April 2026 and
OL,16,FMiddlesbrough in May 2026."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779466274
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough to play in Championship
OL,4,Cplay-off final after Southampton
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,FIt added: "Southampton has a right to
OL,8,Fappeal the Commission's decision in
OL,9,Faccordance with EFL Regulations and
OL,10,Fthe parties are working to try and
OL,11,Fresolve any appeal on Wednesday 20
OL,12,FMay. Subject to the outcome, it could
OL,13,Fresult in a further change to
OL,14,FSaturday's fixture.
OL,16,F"The EFL is now in discussion with all
OL,17,Fthree Clubs regarding the implications
OL,18,Fof today's decision and will make a
OL,19,Ffurther announcement in due course.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779466274
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough to play in Championship
OL,4,Cplay-off final after Southampton
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,F"The Commission's full written reasons
OL,8,Fwill also be published in due course."
OL,10,FReacting to the announcement,
OL,11,FMiddlesbrough said the EFL's verdict
OL,12,Fsent "a clear message for the future
OL,13,Fof our game regarding sporting
OL,14,Fintegrity and conduct."
OL,16,FIt added it was now "focused" on the
OL,17,Fgame against Hull City, which could
OL,18,Fsee them promoted to the Premier
OL,19,FLeague for the first time since the
OL,20,F2016-17 season.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
